title: Judge Dredd - The Judge Child Saga (Complete)
description:
In the year 2102 a dying Psi Division Judge has a precognitive vision that Mega-City One will be destroyed in the year 2120 unless the Judges can find The "Judge Child", a boy called Owen Krysler with extreme telepathic and precognitive powers. Krysler is destined to rule Mega-City One in its direst hour.

The initial quest is set over 26 progs, however, it will take over 18 years for the consequences of that initial quest to play out and see if the Psi-Judge's vision of doom is realised.


01 - The Judge Child Quest (progs 0156-0181)

02 - Block War (prog 0182)

03 - City of the Damned (progs 0393-0406)

04 - Dark Side (progs 1017-1028)

05 - In the Year 2120 (special prog 1077)


Thanks to the original uploaders of the individual editions, in particular Nemesis43.
